quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni Ndaygu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, sifa Ndaygu Makko ngun ko wano tu…ó…óere hara no e mayre pitilol(lampu), pitilol ngol wona e nder biiniiri, biiniiri ndin hara hindi wa'i wa hoodere jalbunde hinde hu…ì…ìa immorde e leggal barkinaangal nebbantewal ngal wonaa funnaangeyankowal ngal wonaa hirnaangeyankowal nebban maggal …óan no …ìadoo jalbude, hay si yiite meemaali …óan, ndaygu e hoore ndaygu, Alla no fewnira ndaygu Makko ngun on mo O Muuyi, Alla no piyana yim…ìe …ìen mise, Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde. @Corrected"
  24,36,E nder cuu…ói …ói Alla du≈ãii(sakkiti) yo darne Innde Makko jantee e nder majji Subunhinanee Mo nder majji ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe
  24,37,"Wor…ìe …ìe njulaaku e ngeyngu maapintaa …óum gaayi ja≈ãtagol Alla e √±imnugol Julde nden e tottu- gol Jakka on, hi…ìe huli √ëalaande nde waylitoytoo e muu…óum …ìer…óe …óen e gii…óe …óen"
  24,38,"Fii yo Alla yo…ìoy…ìe ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude ko …ìe gollunoo kon, O …ìeydana …ìe e ∆Åural Makko ngal. Alla no arsika on mo O Muuyi ko Aldaa hasboore"
  24,39,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen no wa'i wa merere wonunde e boowal, …óon…óaa…óo on no sikka ko nde ndiyam, haa si o arii e mayre o tawataa hay e huunde, o tawa Alla ka Makko O huu…ìinana mo hasboore makko nden, Alla ko O Yaawu…óo Hasboore. @Corrected"
  24,40,"Maa…óum ko wano ni…ìe e maayo luggungo, no suddi ngo benpe∆¥∆¥e no dow maggo benpe∆¥∆¥e no dow majje duule, ni…ìe yoga e majje no e dow yoga, si o yaltinii junngo makko ngon o …ìadotaako yi'ugol ngo. On mo Alla wa…óanaali ndaygu hara o alaa ndaygu"
  24,41,"Enee, a yi'aali wonndema Alla no subuhinanaade Mo …ìen wonu…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi e colli …óin kadi ko saffinii…ói? Gooto kala e …óii gom…óii anndii julde mu'un nden e subuhinaali mu'un …óin, Alla ko O Anndu…óo ko …ìe Huuwata"
  24,42,"Ko Alla heeranii Laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, ko faade ka Alla woni wa…ótinirde nden"
  24,43,"Enee, a yi'aali wonndema Alla hiMo sogga duulere, refti O hawtindira nde, refti O wa…óa nde fawondirnde hi…óa yi'a to…ìo ngon no yalta e nder mayre, ngo jippoo immorde ka kammu, immorde e pelle no e nder mayre marmalle hiMo hewtina …óe on mo O Muuyi, hiMo pottina …óe on mo O Muuyi? Ndaneeri ma∆¥e mayre no do'a na…ìude gii…óe …óen"
  24,44,"Alla hiMo waylita jemma on e √±alorma on, pellet, na wonii e …óum tasakuyee wonannde joomiraa…ìe gii…óe …ìen"
  24,45,"Ko Alla tagii kala daabe hun immorde e ndiyam, no e majji yaarooji reedu muu…óum, no e majji yaarooji koy…óe muu…óm no e majji kadi yaarooji [koy…óe] nayi. Alla hiMo Taga ko O Muuyi, pellet, Alla ko O hattan…óo kala huunde"
  24,46,"Gom…óii Men jippinii Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe, Alla no fewna on mo O muuyii faade e Laawol foccii ngol"
  24,47,"Hi…ìe wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii Alla e Nulaa…óo on, men …óoftike, refti huccita fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe, …ìaawo …óum, …ìen wonaali gom…óin…ìe"
  24,48,"Si …ìe noddaama faade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on fii yo o √±aawu hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, tawa fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe …óuurnii…ìe"
  24,49,"Si tawii ko kam…ìe mari goonga kan, …ìe aray ka makko ko …ìe …óoftii…ìe"
  24,50,"Enee, ko nawnaare woni ka …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe, kaa …ìe sikkiti, kaa …ìe hulu wata Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on too√±u …ìe? Ko woni, …ìee ko kam…ìe woni too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  24,51,"Anndu ko woni konngol gom…óin…ìe …ìen si …ìe noddaama faade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on fii yo o √±aawu hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, ko nde …ìe wi'ata: \"Men nanii men …óoftike.\" ∆Åen …óon ko kam…ìe woni malaa…ìe …ìen"
  24,52,"Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on o huli Alla o rentii [e Lepte Makko …óen] haray …ìen …óon ko kam…ìe woni malaa…ìe …ìen"